Package: gtR
Type: Package
Title: Access the UK Research and Innovation (UKRI) Gateway to Research (GtR) API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shane Jackson
Maintainer: Shane Jackson <shane.jackson@gmx.co.uk>
Description: Simplifies routes to accessing the GtR API by handling some of the repetitive basics of query-writing under the hood. 
